    [1]="Strength ðŸ’ª",[2]="Durability ðŸ›¡ï¸",[3]="Chakra ðŸŒ€",[4]="Sword ðŸ—¡ï¸",[5]="Speed ðŸ’¨",[6]="Agility â˜ï¸"
